# A* Execution Plan for COM5411 BarmBuzz Assignment

This plan outlines the steps to build the automated AD infrastructure, generate the necessary evidence, and write the 3000-word documentation to achieve an A* grade using Pathway 1 (Single-Domain Excellence). Pathway 1 is selected because you have provisioned a single Windows Server, and it meets the criteria by demonstrating deep enterprise-correct security (Delegated Admin, Admin Hygiene, FGPP).

