## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- You will need to run `.\Run_BuildMain.ps1` on your Windows Server VM as Administrator.
- You will then run the provided Pester Tests: `.\Tests\Pester\Invoke-Validation.ps1`.
- If there are failures, you can send me the errors (from the `Evidence\` folder transcrips or Pester results) and I will debug the DSC configuration for you.

### Manual Verification
- Once you run the build on your Windows Server, verify the outputs in the `Evidence\` folder and commit those outputs to your repository before doing your final submission.
